main event: Several witnesses observed six aerial objects on the night of April 28th, 1949.
interesting points: The initial sighting of six objects was made by a couple and a school teacher,The objects were seen flying individually rather than as a group,After a few minutes, more witnesses, including a daughter and grandson, observed four additional objects,All objects were traveling in the same direction,The report was marked with insufficient data for evaluation.
witness description: a couple, a school teacher, a daughter, and a grandson
